<subSubSection box="[199,1413,2009,2036]" pageId="8" pageNumber="529" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1437,893,2036]" box="[199,1413,2009,2036]" pageId="8" pageNumber="529">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,2009,2035]" pageId="8" pageNumber="529">Etymology.</emphasis>
The specific epithet is derived from the Latin 
<emphasis box="[827,932,2010,2035]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="529">stigmosus</emphasis>
, referring to the black spots on the forewing.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
